profile: At SASKA Design, we specialize in custom residential/commercial interior designs and renovations throughout the GTA and Simcoe County. Our mission is to improve the quality of lifestyle by implementing contemporary designs to the nearest satisfaction. We cater our designs to specific requests and go out of our way to make sure that the work we do is a reflection of our client's priorities, wishes, and desires collaborated with budget and timeline. Whether it's a design consultation or a progressive renovation, we are always there to keep the project on the right track in cooperation with professional software to provide high-quality drawings as well as 3D views for better visualization.
